- "Approved comments" are comments that have been marked as `is_approved = 1` in the comments table;
- A reader is considered active if they have at least one comment in the comments table.

- 'Blossomed' refers to works that have at least one approved comment and at least one active marketing material;
- 'Richness' refers to the number of approved comments;
- 'Abundance' refers to the number of active marketing materials.

